sellers, too.";s:11:"group_count";s:1:"1";s:11:"field_count";s:1:"2";s:7:"options";s:6:"a:0:{}";}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":6:{s:10:"field_name";s:15:"speeches_speech";s:4:"type";s:15:"markdown_editor";s:10:"meta_value";s:368:"<strong>Let's Talk Teen Romance! She'll talk about ‚Äúwho‚Äôs buying what‚Äù, YA project taboos,</strong> how YA book covers can boost book sales, and voice/dialogue in young adult fiction. She'll also talk about essential elements she puts into her young adult novels. And, most importantly, she‚Äôll talk candidly about what you can do to break into this hot market.";s:11:"group_count";s:1:"1";s:11:"field_count";s:1:"3";s:7:"options";s:6:"a:0:{}";}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":6:{s:10:"field_name";s:15:"speeches_speech";s:4:"type";s:15:"markdown_editor";s:10:"meta_value";s:328:"<strong>Writing Timeless Teen Dialogue:</strong> Simone Elkeles will show you how to write humorous, active, realistic dialogue in your teen manuscripts. She‚Äôll give examples of teen dialogue that works and what doesn‚Äôt work, along with exercises on using dialogue and internal thoughts to create realistic teen characters. ";s:11:"group_count";s:1:"1";s:11:"field_count";s:1:"4";s:7:"options";s:6:"a:0:{}";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":6:{s:10:"field_name";s:15:"speeches_speech";s:4:"type";s:15:"markdown_editor";s:10:"meta_value";s:387:"<strong>Marketing Your Novel ‚Äì Secrets of a Marketing Queen: </strong>In addition to writing great teen romances, Simone attributes her tireless dedication to marketing to boost book sales a big part of the success of her books.  Come to this workshop and learn all that Simone has done, marketing-wise, to help catapult her to one of the biggest names in the young adult romance genre";s:11:"group_count";s:1:"1";s:11:"field_count";s:1:"5";s:7:"options";s:6:"a:0:{}";}}s:8:"col_info";a:6:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":13:{s:4:"name";s:10:"field_name";s:5:"table";s:1:"m";s:3:"def";s:0:"";s:10:"max_length";i:15;s:8:"not_null";i:1;s:11:"primary_key";i:0;s:12:"multiple_key";i:0;s:1